race.comment: PRESSIPITATING (7) ran on fairly first-up at Grafton over this trip in a race that has thrown up plenty of subsequent winners. Disappointed last time at Ballina over 1300m but back at this distance she is a definite threat. HERE'S MASON (2) is a 24-start maiden whose recent form over longer trips has been plain. Raced here once over 1000m and filled a placing. Each-way prospects. CASTLE OF CARDS (5) is back from a 19-week spell. Best figure last prep was over this trip at Grafton when a closing fourth. Can play a role with a repeat of that effort. LULU A NATURAL (6) on a nine-day back-up is one for trifectas and first fours.
